content:
, 2016
Simply the best. Before this game I used to play Soldiers Heroes of World War 2 (SHOWW2 for short) when I was 9 years old, which was the 1st ever Men of War game! I was pretty sad when I found out that nobody played that MP game and all the units that went into the waste. But then I found out that there was this series called Men of War and now I'm reliving my dream. After playing this game I cannot and I repeat CAN NOT go back to Company of Heroes 2 cause it's unrealistic and I'm so used to damaging the machines that I find it unrealistic how those units suck up damage and the HP bar. All in all If you enjoy realistic games and teamwork then this game is for you.

Watch out for my tiger c;
